Package: axR
Title: Serial Communication and Data Retrieval for Axivity Devices
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lucas", "França",
           email = "lucas.franca@northumbria.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0853-1319")))
Description: Serial (CDC/COM port) communication with Axivity AX3/AX6
    accelerometer devices for device discovery, configuration, and reset,
    plus retrieval of recorded data over the device's USB mass storage
    interface. Communicates using the documented Open Movement serial
    command protocol. Does not parse '.cwa' files; that is left to
    downstream packages (see mrpheus, zeitR). Part of the Circadia Lab
    R ecosystem.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
